@startuml state-machines
' ============================================================
' AlharisTech Platform — Aggregate State Machine Diagrams
' Order, Ticket, CommerceOrder, Invoice, User Account
' ============================================================

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 10

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #D4E6F1
  BorderColor #2980B9
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  FontSize 10
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  BorderColor #F1C40F
  FontSize 9
}

skinparam arrow {
  FontSize 9
}

title **AlharisTech Platform — Aggregate State Machines**
title **آلات الحالة للتجميعات الرئيسية — الطلبات، التذاكر، الفواتير، الحسابات**

' ============================================================
' 1. SERVICE ORDER STATE MACHINE
' ============================================================

state "**Service Order** (service.orders)" as OrderTitle #F4F6F7

state "draft\nمسودة" as OrderDraft
state "pending\nقيد الانتظار" as OrderPending
state "in_review\nقيد المراجعة" as OrderReview
state "in_progress\nقيد المعالجة" as OrderProgress
state "completed\nمكتمل" as OrderCompleted #D5F5E3
state "cancelled\nملغي" as OrderCancelled #FADBD8
state "rejected\nمرفوض" as OrderRejected #FADBD8

OrderTitle -down-> OrderDraft

[*] -down-> OrderDraft : Customer starts order

OrderDraft --> OrderPending : submitOrder()\n▪ Customer submits form + documents\n▪ Event: OrderPlaced

OrderPending --> OrderReview : assignEmployee()\n▪ Admin/Manager assigns employee\n▪ Event: OrderAssigned\n▪ Auto-transition on assignment

OrderPending --> OrderCancelled : cancelOrder()\n▪ Customer cancels before review\n▪ Guard: cancel_reason required

OrderPending --> OrderRejected : rejectOrder()\n▪ Employee rejects application\n▪ Guard: rejection note required

OrderReview --> OrderProgress : startProcessing()\n▪ Employee begins work\n▪ Guard: ALL documents verified = true\n▪ Event: OrderStatusChanged

OrderReview --> OrderPending : requestClarification()\n▪ Employee needs more documents\n▪ Event: OrderStatusChanged\n▪ Customer notified to upload

OrderReview --> OrderCancelled : adminCancel()\n▪ Admin cancels during review\n▪ Guard: cancel_reason required

OrderReview --> OrderRejected : rejectOrder()\n▪ Employee rejects\n▪ Guard: rejection note required

OrderProgress --> OrderCompleted : completeOrder()\n▪ Employee finishes work\n▪ Guard: all docs verified\n▪ Event: OrderCompleted\n▪ Sets completed_at = NOW()\n▪ Triggers rating request

OrderProgress --> OrderCancelled : adminCancel()\n▪ Admin cancels during processing\n▪ Guard: cancel_reason required

OrderCompleted --> [*] : TERMINAL

OrderCancelled --> OrderPending : adminReopen()\n▪ Admin only\n▪ Event: OrderStatusChanged

OrderRejected --> OrderPending : adminReopen()\n▪ Admin only\n▪ Event: OrderStatusChanged

note right of OrderCancelled
  **Cancelled/Rejected can be**
  **reopened only by Admin.**
  reopened → pending
  Customer can resubmit.
endnote

' ============================================================
' 2. SUPPORT TICKET STATE MACHINE
' ============================================================

state "**Support Ticket** (support.tickets)" as TicketTitle #F4F6F7

state "open\nمفتوح" as TicketOpen
state "in_progress\nقيد المعالجة" as TicketProgress
state "waiting_customer\nبانتظار العميل" as TicketWaiting
state "resolved\nتم الحل" as TicketResolved #D5F5E3
state "closed\nمغلق" as TicketClosed #D5F5E3
state "reopened\nمعاد فتحه" as TicketReopened

TicketTitle -down-> TicketOpen

[*] -down-> TicketOpen : Customer creates ticket\n▪ Priority auto-assigned\n▪ SLA deadlines computed\n▪ Event: TicketOpened

TicketOpen --> TicketProgress : assignOrStart()\n▪ Manager assigns employee\n▪ OR employee takes action\n▪ Event: TicketAssigned

TicketOpen --> TicketResolved : quickResolve()\n▪ Simple issue, resolved immediately\n▪ Event: TicketResolved

TicketProgress --> TicketWaiting : needCustomerInput()\n▪ Employee needs customer info\n▪ Event: TicketStatusChanged

TicketProgress --> TicketResolved : resolveTicket()\n▪ Employee provides solution\n▪ Sets resolved_at = NOW()\n▪ Event: TicketResolved

TicketWaiting --> TicketProgress : customerReply()\n▪ AUTO on customer message\n▪ Event: TicketMessageAdded\n▪ Event: TicketStatusChanged

TicketWaiting --> TicketResolved : resolveFromWaiting()\n▪ Employee resolves while waiting\n▪ Event: TicketResolved

TicketResolved --> TicketClosed : autoClose()\n▪ System cron (every 15 min)\n▪ Guard: updated_at > 72 hours\n▪ Sets closed_at = NOW()\n▪ Event: TicketClosed

TicketResolved --> TicketReopened : customerReopen()\n▪ Guard: NOW() - resolved_at < 7 days\n▪ Increments reopened_count\n▪ Event: TicketReopened

TicketClosed --> TicketReopened : customerReopen()\n▪ Guard: NOW() - closed_at < 7 days\n▪ Event: TicketReopened

TicketReopened --> TicketProgress : autoTransition()\n▪ Ticket resumes with same assignee

note right of TicketClosed
  **Reopen Window: 7 calendar days.**
  After 7 days: create new ticket
  referencing old ticket.
  Error: REOPEN_WINDOW_EXPIRED
endnote

note right of TicketOpen
  **Admin Force-Close:**
  Any status → closed
  Only Admin role.
  Reason required.
endnote

' ============================================================
' 3. COMMERCE ORDER STATE MACHINE
' ============================================================

state "**Commerce Order** (commerce.orders)" as ComOrderTitle #F4F6F7

state "pending\nقيد الانتظار" as ComPending
state "confirmed\nمؤكد" as ComConfirmed
state "processing\nقيد التجهيز" as ComProcessing
state "shipped\nتم الشحن" as ComShipped
state "delivered\nتم التسليم" as ComDelivered #D5F5E3
state "cancelled\nملغي" as ComCancelled #FADBD8
state "refunded\nمسترجع" as ComRefunded #FADBD8

ComOrderTitle -down-> ComPending

[*] -down-> ComPending : Customer completes checkout\n▪ Cart validated\n▪ Payment initiated\n▪ Event: OrderPlaced

ComPending --> ComConfirmed : paymentSucceeded()\n▪ Payment verified (sync or webhook)\n▪ Guard: payment_status = 'paid'\n▪ Sets placed_at = NOW()\n▪ Event: PaymentCompleted

ComPending --> ComCancelled : paymentFailedOrTimeout()\n▪ Payment failed or 30min timeout\n▪ Guard: cancel_reason required\n▪ Event: OrderCancelled\n▪ Cart re-activated for retry

ComConfirmed --> ComProcessing : beginFulfillment()\n▪ Inventory reserved\n▪ Guard: all items in stock\n▪ Event: InventoryReserved

ComConfirmed --> ComCancelled : adminCancel()\n▪ Admin cancels before processing\n▪ Guard: cancel_reason required\n▪ Event: OrderCancelled\n▪ Inventory released

ComProcessing --> ComShipped : shipOrder()\n▪ Tracking number assigned\n▪ Sets shipped_at = NOW()\n▪ Sets estimated_delivery\n▪ Event: ShipmentCreated

ComShipped --> ComDelivered : deliveryConfirmed()\n▪ Carrier confirms delivery\n▪ Auto on tracking update\n▪ Sets delivered_at = NOW()\n▪ Event: ShipmentDelivered

ComDelivered --> ComRefunded : processRefund()\n▪ Customer return/refund\n▪ Refund via payment gateway\n▪ Inventory released\n▪ Event: OrderRefunded

ComCancelled --> [*] : TERMINAL
ComRefunded --> [*] : TERMINAL

note right of ComShipped
  **Cannot cancel after shipped.**
  Must use refund process.
endnote

' ============================================================
' 4. INVOICE STATE MACHINE
' ============================================================

state "**Invoice** (billing.invoices)" as InvTitle #F4F6F7

state "draft\nمسودة" as InvDraft
state "sent\nمرسلة" as InvSent
state "paid\nمدفوعة" as InvPaid #D5F5E3
state "overdue\nمتأخرة" as InvOverdue #FADBD8
state "void\nملغاة" as InvVoid #FADBD8

InvTitle -down-> InvDraft

[*] -down-> InvDraft : System generates invoice\n▪ Triggered by OrderPlaced event\n▪ Amount from order total

InvDraft --> InvSent : sendInvoice()\n▪ Invoice finalized and sent\n▪ Customer receives email/SMS

InvSent --> InvPaid : paymentReceived()\n▪ Payment confirmed via gateway\n▪ Sets paid_at = NOW()\n▪ Event: InvoicePaid

InvSent --> InvOverdue : paymentDeadlineExceeded()\n▪ Cron: due_date < NOW()\n▪ AND payment_status != 'paid'\n▪ Event: InvoiceOverdue\n▪ Late payment reminder sent

InvOverdue --> InvPaid : latePaymentReceived()\n▪ Payment received after due date\n▪ May include late fees

InvSent --> InvVoid : voidInvoice()\n▪ Order cancelled → void\n▪ Admin can manually void\n▪ Guard: cannot void paid invoice

InvDraft --> InvVoid : voidDraft()\n▪ Draft discarded

InvPaid --> [*] : TERMINAL
InvVoid --> [*] : TERMINAL

' ============================================================
' 5. USER ACCOUNT STATE MACHINE
' ============================================================

state "**User Account** (identity.users)" as UserTitle #F4F6F7

state "unverified\nغير مفعل" as UserUnverified
state "active\nنشط" as UserActive #D5F5E3
state "locked\nمقفل" as UserLocked #FADBD8
state "disabled\nمعطل" as UserDisabled #FADBD8

UserTitle -down-> UserUnverified

[*] -down-> UserUnverified : User registers\n▪ Role: customer (default)\n▪ is_verified: false\n▪ Event: UserRegistered

UserUnverified --> UserActive : verifyEmail()\n▪ Email verification token (24h TTL)\n▪ Sets is_verified = true\n▪ Event: UserVerified

UserUnverified --> UserActive : login()\n▪ Login allowed even if unverified\n▪ Verification is optional for login

UserActive --> UserLocked : exceedLoginAttempts()\n▪ Guard: failed_login_attempts ≥ 5\n▪ Sets locked_until = NOW() + 30 min\n▪ Event: AccountLocked\n▪ Security alert sent

UserLocked --> UserActive : lockTimeoutExpired()\n▪ Guard: NOW() > locked_until\n▪ Auto-unlock after 30 minutes\n▪ Resets failed_login_attempts = 0

UserActive --> UserDisabled : adminDisable()\n▪ Admin disables account\n▪ Revokes ALL sessions\n▪ Event: AccountDisabled

UserDisabled --> UserActive : adminEnable()\n▪ Admin re-enables account\n▪ User can login again

note right of UserLocked
  **Password Reset:**
  User stays in current state.
  Password change revokes
  all refresh tokens except
  current session.
endnote

' ============================================================
' SUMMARY TABLE
' ============================================================

note bottom of UserDisabled
  **= Transition Summary =**
  |= Aggregate |= Total States |= Terminal States |= Auto Transitions =
  | Service Order | 7 | completed, cancelled, rejected | pending→in_review (on assign) |
  | Support Ticket | 6 | closed | resolved→closed (72h), waiting→in_progress (on reply) |
  | Commerce Order | 7 | cancelled, refunded | shipped→delivered (on tracking), pending→cancelled (30min timeout) |
  | Invoice | 5 | paid, void | sent→overdue (past due_date) |
  | User Account | 4 | disabled | locked→active (after 30min) |
endnote

@enduml
